import App from './App.vue'
import Vue from 'vue'
import router from './router/router'
import AdminApp from './AdminApp.vue'
import router2 from './router/router2'


Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  router,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
